self.title: CDISC CDASH Unit of Measure for Flow Rate Terminology

definition: A terminology subset of the CDISC SDTM Unit codelist created for CDASH Unit of Measure for Flow Rate codelist. (NCI)
name: Unit of Measure for Flow Rate
preferredTerm: CDISC CDASH Unit of Measure for Flow Rate Terminology
synonyms: Unit of Measure for Flow Rate

terms.definition: A unit of flow rate equal to one milliliter per minute.
A unit of substance flow rate equal to one millimole per day.
A unit of mass flow rate equal to one microgram per day.
A unit of mass flow rate equal to one microgram per minute.
A unit of substance flow rate equal to one micromole per day.
